AUDIO: 'hard to analyze what exactly this is. Typically,&nbsp; these signals can be very messy and noisy. Plus,&nbsp;&nbsp; the electrode layout could be different between&nbsp; different subjects and different places. Plus,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

